{"tid":377704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐卡素大學證實中國總領館介入教材「傷害中國學生感情」事件","createTime":"2017-08-28T01:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T03:49:48.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1704e16366447a2aef32a9509badf4681e40c7","tid":377704,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.sbs.com.au/yourlanguage/cantonese/zh-hant/article/2017/08/28/jiao-cai-shi-jian-da-xue-zheng-shi-zhong-guo-zong-ling-guan-jie-ru\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fyourlanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Farticle%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2Fjiao-cai-shi-jian-da-xue-zheng-shi-zhong-guo-zong-ling-guan-jie-ru&d=4B2rI1UwQJXGe7zbu6YXSF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6157a65a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sbs.com.au/yourlanguage/cantonese/zh-hant/article/2017/08/28/jiao-cai-shi-jian-da-xue-zheng-shi-zhong-guo-zong-ling-guan-jie-ru</a><br />\n<br />\n紐卡素大學有中國留學生指教材「傷害中國學生感情」事件，中國駐雪梨總領事館介入，有澳洲傳媒稱事件反映中國政府的影響力正延伸至校園。<br />\n<br />\n《澳洲人日報》引述紐卡素大學證實，中國駐雪梨總領館有就事件接觸大學。有報導稱，總領館接觸大學，部分原因是事件觸及「一個中國的底線」和「嚴重傷害中國學生感情」。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上星期，一名大學講師在教材圖表中將台灣及香港列作個別國家，與中國分開處理。講師對當場抗議的學生表示，會在課後處理，學生則把課後談話內容錄下，交給一家在澳洲的中文傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n事件是 5 月以來第 4 宗中國留學生不滿教學內容引起的風波。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，紐卡素大學被問到在「一中」問題上的立場。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">報導未有提及具體教材，但很多調查報告，如評估貪污水平的世界透明指數，都將台港澳與中國分開，當作個別國家或地區處理。<br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n較早前，雪梨大學一名中國留學生不滿一名講師採用一張世界地圖，把中印爭議邊界列為印度國境。"},{"pid":"2c3f976569880a2f9b1af69efa3a5eb85e56bec9","tid":377704,"uid":54959,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T01:23:44.000Z","msg":"支那人上至政府下至蟻民都係仆街"},{"pid":"a6ee3fc89863a85e09cefd0a37806a697fbc9b46","tid":377704,"uid":35430,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T01:55:48.000Z","msg":"引入咁多大陸學生賺大陸錢<br />\n畀大陸滲透只係遲早問題<br />\n我講過世界上咩政府咩人都可以信，只有大陸政權同黃皮狗唔可以信，大中華毒一上腦就會埋邊大陸就算係移民二代都一樣<br />\n哩樣賤種炎黃基因冇500年都移除唔到"},{"pid":"1cda9e1088fe571f5ddfdc22c485453e68aaa658","tid":377704,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:01:41.000Z","msg":"支那狗出國邊一次唔柒"},{"pid":"be23bfa9220ea6a444d4789f28d2274e29592650","tid":377704,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那知唔知咩叫學術自由，同現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果個學生識唔識分咩叫nation, 咩叫country<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩叫jurisdiction"},{"pid":"7625f8522f8b1d73bbf0e97cad66d7b63c8c7b17","tid":377704,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"CSSA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db1dd0e45883a467409425736d02e914cf46d43","tid":377704,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:19:34.000Z","msg":"西方世界繼續包容隻大怪物啦"},{"pid":"d34dc6241cb9960d8d70344b11f38707f3ec7288","tid":377704,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"介入學術自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02566ec5f23543ea39ec4d80fafa2baecc024f9","tid":377704,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>引入咁多大陸學生賺大陸錢<br />\n畀大陸滲透只係遲早問題<br />\n我講過世界上咩政府咩人都可以信，只有大陸政權同黃皮狗唔可以信，大中華毒一上腦就會埋邊大陸就算係移民二代都一樣<br />\n哩樣賤種炎黃基因冇500年都移除唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhi黃皮狗"},{"pid":"2e305adc64481eba3c5109155d169a9b8b82d211","tid":377704,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T02:37:17.000Z","msg":"引狼入室"},{"pid":"4916431108882c48b1bb89676050066b9520ff99","tid":3777